DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-143. In re Resignation of Schaner.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Brian Keith Schaner, Attorney Registration No. 0005282, last known address in Cleveland Heights, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of February 12, 1998, to wit, failure to pay publication costs in the amount of $351.48 on or before April 26, 2000.
